overview: It's that instant attraction that sends the signal, blood coursing from your brain to your bulge as you eye his imposing image. The twitch hits like lightening, imploring you to act on your Impulse.  Come closer... TitanMen exclusives Jessy Ares, Dario Beck, Philippe Ferro and Hunter Marx lead a cast of throbbing bods ready to help with your urge.
title: Impulse
